	   <tr><td colspan=2>Not to nitpick, but... the comment about &quot;getting as good of prices here as anywhere&quot; is not quite accurate. The OT vendors are &quot;cheap&quot; vendors, who overcharge and give little in return for sold items. This makes OT a very poor place to offload loot.<br><br>HOWEVER, there is a port to the Plane of Knowlege just outside the outpost, near Alchemist Granika. The merchants there will pay you just fine.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
